OL,5, Next has cut sick pay for unvaccinated 
OL,6, staff who must self-isolate because of 
OL,7, Covid exposure, the BBC has learned.   
OL,9,FUnvaccinated staff will still get full 
OL,10,Fsick pay if they test positive for the 
OL,11,Fvirus.                                 
OL,13,FThe retailer's move follows a similar  
OL,14,Fone by Ikea. Next acknowledged it was  
OL,15,Fan "emotive topic" but said it had to  
OL,16,Fbalance staff and shareholder needs.   
OL,18,FIt comes as employers face mass        
OL,19,Fabsences due to the rapid spread of the
OL,20,FOmicron variant.                       
